(91, 'shipping_policy', '<h2><strong>Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This document sets out the Shipping Policy that shall apply to you (&ldquo;You&rdquo; or &ldquo;Your&rdquo; or &ldquo;User&rdquo;), as the user of the website https://yehloapp.com (&ldquo;Website&rdquo;), and/or the mobile application called YEHLO, (collectively, &ldquo;Platform&rdquo;) which is owned and operated by UQuick Ecommerce Private Limited (&ldquo;We&rdquo; or &ldquo;Us&rdquo; or &ldquo;Company&rdquo;), a company incorporated under the provisions of the Companies Act, 2013 having its registered office at H 211, First Floor, Sector 63, Noida Gautam Buddha Nagar, UttarPradesh 201301 India. This Privacy Policy, as amended from time to time, is to be read along with the Terms of Use as available on the Website.<br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\nDELIVERY</strong><br />\r\nOnce we process your order, dispatch of goods will be initiated through courier, postal or other means of transport as deemed fit, through our trusted delivery partner. Our delivery partners may make up to 3 [three] attempts to deliver the Products. If the premises are locked or if the nominated recipients are not available, it will be treated as undeliverable and the courier will initiate return of Products to Company. In case of such multiple delivery failures, we will consider the Order as cancelled.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FAQ&rsquo;s</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>What are the shipping options for my order?</strong><br />\r\nWe currently offer only one shipping option.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is the estimated delivery time?</strong><br />\r\nYour Products are expected to be delivered on same day or within 3-10 business days (depending on the location) after the Products have been dispatched and picked up by our delivery partner. Business days exclude Sundays and public holidays. Delivery timelines may vary depending on your location. The estimated delivery time will be provided on the Product page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How are Products packaged?</strong><br />\r\nProducts shall be packed in boxes, paper bags and/or bubble wraps. However, in case of select Products where additional packaging is required to secure the Product from transit damage, additional packaging may be added.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can I track my order?</strong><br />\r\nOnce your order is dispatched, you shall receive an email/SMS on the registered email id/ number provided by you at the time of registration, with the tracking number and courier company that is processing your order. You can also track your parcel here.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How do I check the current status of my order?</strong><br />\r\nYou can check the status of your order by visiting the &ldquo;My Orders&rdquo; section and viewing your specific order.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do you ship to international locations?</strong><br />\r\nWe currently ship only within India and do not ship to any international location.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Can I change my delivery address after I place an order?</strong><br />\r\nCurrently, we don&rsquo;t allow change of address after an order is placed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'admin_landing_page', '2024-05-18 18:52:29', '2024-06-06 11:53:23'),
(92, 'about_us', '<p>Shop for groceries, food, medicines, electronics and more from stores near you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yehlo lets you shop for all your needs from stores near you! Get groceries, food, medicines, electronics and more delivered right to your doorstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Look for supermarkets, specialty stores and more in your neighbourhood. Find a wide variety of products from your favourite local stores, with a selection of more than 20,000 items, including - farm fresh produce, staples, grains, meat &amp; fish, oil &amp; ghee, dry fruits, pet supplies, baby care, cleaning supplies, stationery, personal care, gourmet and more at the best prices. Create a cart with items from regional, private label and national brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can search for your favourite items in each store and place orders directly at the store. Your order will be delivered right to your doorstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can pay for your orders with safe and secure digital payments powered by PhonePe. You can pay with your preferred payment option including UPI, wallet, gift vouchers, credit cards and debit cards. Shop hassle free with instant refunds and easy returns.</p>', 'admin_landing_page', '2024-05-18 18:54:42', '2024-05-18 18:54:42'),
