(98, 'seller_description', 'You are eligible to get paid for the order 7 days after the order is delivered. yehlo ensures payment for your sales (minus the Yehlo Seller fees) is deposited securely into your bank account every 7 days, including your Pay on Delivery orders. Eligible sellers will also receive options for faster payment cycles.  You can view your deposited balance along with tips to grow and expand your business in your Seller Central account.  NOTE: The above information is applicable for new sellers who will join the \"Standard\" level in the yehlo STEP program. As sellers move up levels, they will be able to unlock multiple benefits including fee waivers, account management faster disbursement cycles, & more.', 'admin_landing_page', '2024-06-05 15:26:21', '2024-06-06 10:45:07'),
